{"tid":504551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好好珍惜俾到家嘅感覺你嘅人","createTime":"2017-12-20T06:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T06:56:57.000Z","uid":27741,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cec4ed67b3191cfbd0de8ac057cfc9aebbfd48ce","tid":504551,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"無論係真實血緣上有關係嘅人、另一半定係朋友<br />\n喺生活中俾到家人感覺你嘅人其實真係唔多 <br />\n有佢地你真係好幸運好幸福<br />\n得閒關心下錫下佢地 唔好take it for granted<br />\n感情係雙方嘅付出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">多謝男朋友令我依個家庭唔太開心嘅人<br />\n覺得我切切實實擁有一個愛錫我嘅屋企人 <br />\n更加分享你原本有嘅家庭溫暖俾我<br />\n<br />\n多謝兩個朋友喺我抑鬱焦慮之時扶持我<br />\n當我又黎料嘅時候 借個膊頭俾我 <br />\n甚至擔心我唔食野 煮埋飯俾我 <br />\n幫埋我做埋家務 廁所都洗埋 我真係感動到唔知講咩好</span>"},{"pid":"2f1c2c8ec8978c7b7ce4e6321054c52414e43bd4","tid":504551,"uid":53794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣"},{"pid":"6eda53db80a4eb63a789670e54623e578ede815f","tid":504551,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"a1c58b5abe3e4ec039db4f3e921d3905a01b1b30","tid":504551,"uid":76105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"女朋友會煮定飯 準備我鐘意食既餸<br />\n等我放工返屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日講爛gag氹我笑<br />\n想永遠保護佢，俾一個家佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但已散 已經搵唔番類似感覺既人 </span></span>"},{"pid":"14c93c9efaf47969b1799a891140bafefb2d91b6","tid":504551,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友會煮定飯 準備我鐘意食既餸<br />\n等我放工返屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日講爛gag氹我笑<br />\n想永遠保護佢，俾一個家佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但已散 已經搵唔番類似感覺既人